  "doc_id": "prion_0570",
  "text": "In an electron microscopic study of brain biopsy material from a case with Creutzfeldt-Jakob disease intranuclear vacuoles containing membrano-vesicular structures were found.\nTo our knowledge this finding has not been previously reported in human spongiform encephalopathies.\nIt may represent a specific alteration associated with Creutzfeldt-Jakob disease, and suggests the possibility of nuclear infection.",
